  <summary date="2019-05-16T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Tax Fairness for Tribal Youth Act of 2019

This bill treats certain payments made by Indian tribal governments to children as earned income of the child for the purposes of the kiddie tax (the tax on the unearned income of children). This has the effect of exempting the payments from the tax. The bill applies to taxable years beginning after December 31, 2017.</summary>
